{"id":193,"ayahs":[{"number":37,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا ٱلنَّسِىٓءُ زِيَادَةٌۭ فِى ٱلْكُفْرِ ۖ يُضَلُّ بِهِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ يُحِلُّونَهُۥ عَامًۭا وَيُحَرِّمُونَهُۥ عَامًۭا لِّيُوَاطِـُٔوا۟ عِدَّةَ مَا حَرَّمَ ٱللَّهُ فَيُحِلُّوا۟ مَا حَرَّمَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ زُيِّنَ لَهُمْ سُوٓءُ أَعْمَٰلِهِمْ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ","translation":"The intercalation [of months] is but one more instance of [their] refusal to acknowledge the truth- [a means] by which those who are bent on denying the truth are led astray. They declare this [intercalation] to be permissible in one year and forbidden in [another] year, in order to conform [outwardly] to the number of months which God has hallowed: and thus they make allowable what God has forbidden. Goodly seems unto them the evil of their own doings, since God does not grace with His guidance people who refuse to acknowledge the truth.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1272.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":38842,"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","translation":"প্রকৃতপক্ষে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38843,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنَّسِىٓءُ","translation":"নাসী (অর্থাৎ হারাম মাসকে পিছিয়ে দেয়া)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38844,"position":3,"arabic":"زِيَادَةٌۭ","translation":"(আরও) বাড়িয়ে দেয়া","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38845,"position":4,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38846,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْكُفْرِ ۖ","translation":"অবিশ্বাসের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38848,"position":6,"arabic":"يُضَلُّ","translation":"পথভ্রষ্ট করা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38849,"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِ","translation":"দিয়ে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38850,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদেরকে) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38851,"position":9,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অবিশ্বাস করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38852,"position":10,"arabic":"يُحِلُّونَهُۥ","translation":"হালাল করে তারা তা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38853,"position":11,"arabic":"عَامًۭا","translation":"কোনো বছর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38854,"position":12,"arabic":"وَيُحَرِّمُونَهُۥ","translation":"আবার (প্রয়োজনে) হারাম করে তারা তা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38855,"position":13,"arabic":"عَامًۭا","translation":"(অন্য) কোনো বছর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38856,"position":14,"arabic":"لِّيُوَاطِـُٔوا۟","translation":"যেন তারা পুরো করে নিতে পারে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38857,"position":15,"arabic":"عِدَّةَ","translation":"সংখ্যা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38858,"position":16,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38859,"position":17,"arabic":"حَرَّمَ","translation":"হারাম করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38860,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38861,"position":19,"arabic":"فَيُحِلُّوا۟","translation":"তাই তারা হালাল করে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38862,"position":20,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38863,"position":21,"arabic":"حَرَّمَ","translation":"হারাম করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38864,"position":22,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۚ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38866,"position":23,"arabic":"زُيِّنَ","translation":"শোভনীয় করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38867,"position":24,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"জন্যে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38868,"position":25,"arabic":"سُوٓءُ","translation":"মন্দ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38869,"position":26,"arabic":"أَعْمَـٰلِهِمْ ۗ","translation":"কাজগুলো তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38871,"position":27,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"আর আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38872,"position":28,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38873,"position":29,"arabic":"يَهْدِى","translation":"সঠিক পথ দেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38874,"position":30,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمَ","translation":"সম্প্রদায়কে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38875,"position":31,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"সত্য অমান্যকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_037_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38876,"position":32,"arabic":"٣٧","translation":"(৩৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":38,"arabic":"يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوا۟ مَا لَكُمْ إِذَا قِيلَ لَكُمُ ٱنفِرُوا۟ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ ٱثَّاقَلْتُمْ إِلَى ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ أَرَضِيتُم بِٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا مِنَ ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ ۚ فَمَا مَتَٰعُ ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ ٱلدُّنْيَا فِى ٱلْءَاخِرَةِ إِلَّا قَلِيلٌ","translation":"O YOU who have attained to faith! What is amiss with you that, when you are called upon, \"Go forth to war in God's cause,\" you cling heavily to the earth? Would you content yourselves with [the comforts of] this worldly life in preference to [the good of] the life to come? But the enjoyment of life in this world is but a paltry thing when compared with the life to come!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1273.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":39744,"position":1,"arabic":"يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا","translation":"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39745,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39746,"position":3,"arabic":"ءَامَنُوا۟","translation":"ঈমান এনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39747,"position":4,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39748,"position":5,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39749,"position":6,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39750,"position":7,"arabic":"قِيلَ","translation":"বলা হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39751,"position":8,"arabic":"لَكُمُ","translation":"উদ্দেশ্যে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39752,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱنفِرُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা বের হও","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39753,"position":10,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39754,"position":11,"arabic":"سَبِيلِ","translation":"পথের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39755,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39756,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱثَّاقَلْتُمْ","translation":"বোঝার ভার নুয়ে পড়ছো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39757,"position":14,"arabic":"إِلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39758,"position":15,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","translation":"জমিনের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39760,"position":16,"arabic":"أَرَضِيتُم","translation":"কি সন্তুষ্ট হয়েছো তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39761,"position":17,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَيَوٰةِ","translation":"নিয়ে জীবন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39762,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পার্থিব","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39763,"position":19,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"পরিবর্তে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39764,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ ۚ","translation":"আখেরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39766,"position":21,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"অথচ নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39767,"position":22,"arabic":"مَتَـٰعُ","translation":"ভোগ সামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39768,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْحَيَوٰةِ","translation":"জীবনের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39769,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পার্থিব","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39770,"position":25,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"তুলনায়","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39771,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","translation":"আখেরাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39772,"position":27,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39773,"position":28,"arabic":"قَلِيلٌ","translation":"অতি তুচ্ছ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_038_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":39774,"position":29,"arabic":"٣٨","translation":"(৩৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":39,"arabic":"إِلَّا تَنفِرُوا۟ يُعَذِّبْكُمْ عَذَابًا أَلِيمًۭا وَيَسْتَبْدِلْ قَوْمًا غَيْرَكُمْ وَلَا تَضُرُّوهُ شَيْـًۭٔا ۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَىْءٍۢ قَدِيرٌ","translation":"If you do not go forth to war [in God's cause], He will chastise you with grievous chastisement, and will place another people in your stead - whereas you shall in no wise harm Him: for, God has the power to will anything.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1274.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":40544,"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"যদি না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40545,"position":2,"arabic":"تَنفِرُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা বের হও","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40546,"position":3,"arabic":"يُعَذِّبْكُمْ","translation":"তিনি শাস্তি দিবেন তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40547,"position":4,"arabic":"عَذَابًا","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40548,"position":5,"arabic":"أَلِيمًۭا","translation":"বড় কষ্টদায়ক","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40549,"position":6,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَبْدِلْ","translation":"ও তিনি পরিবর্তন করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40550,"position":7,"arabic":"قَوْمًا","translation":"(অন্য) জাতিকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40551,"position":8,"arabic":"غَيْرَكُمْ","translation":"ছাড়া তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40552,"position":9,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40553,"position":10,"arabic":"تَضُرُّوهُ","translation":"তার তোমরা ক্ষতি করতে পারবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40554,"position":11,"arabic":"شَيْـًۭٔا ۗ","translation":"কিছুমাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40556,"position":12,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40557,"position":13,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40558,"position":14,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"সব","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40559,"position":15,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ","translation":"কিছুর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40560,"position":16,"arabic":"قَدِيرٌ","translation":"সর্বশক্তিমান","audioUrl":"wbw/009_039_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40561,"position":17,"arabic":"٣٩","translation":"(৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":40,"arabic":"إِلَّا تَنصُرُوهُ فَقَدْ نَصَرَهُ ٱللَّهُ إِذْ أَخْرَجَهُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ ثَانِىَ ٱثْنَيْنِ إِذْ هُمَا فِى ٱلْغَارِ إِذْ يَقُولُ لِصَٰحِبِهِۦ لَا تَحْزَنْ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ مَعَنَا ۖ فَأَنزَلَ ٱللَّهُ سَكِينَتَهُۥ عَلَيْهِ وَأَيَّدَهُۥ بِجُنُودٍۢ لَّمْ تَرَوْهَا وَجَعَلَ كَلِمَةَ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ ٱلسُّفْلَىٰ ۗ وَكَلِمَةُ ٱللَّهِ هِىَ ٱلْعُلْيَا ۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَزِيزٌ حَكِيمٌ","translation":"If you do not succour the Apostle, then [know that God will do so -just as] God succoured him at the time when those who were bent on denying the truth drove him away, [and he was but] one of two: when these two were [hiding] in the cave, [and] the Apostle said to his companion, \"Grieve not: verily, God is with us.\" And thereupon God bestowed upon him from on high His (gift of] inner peace, and brought utterly low the cause of those who were bent on denying the truth, whereas the cause of God remained supreme: for God is almighty, wise.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1275.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":41316,"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"যদি না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_040_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41317,"position":2,"arabic":"تَنصُرُوهُ","translation":"তোমরা সাহায্য করো তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_040_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41318,"position":3,"arabic":"فَقَدْ","translation":"তবে নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/009_040_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41319,"position":4,"arabic":"نَصَرَهُ","translation":"সাহায্য করেছেন তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_040_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41320,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_040_005.mp3","char